data.description: Great opportunity to put your touches on this two story home and enjoy small town living!  Newer flooring in living room and new carpet on stairs.  The spacious kitchen is big enough for your custom island or seating.  Separate dining area off kitchen/living area. First floor laundry and half bath. Small fenced in area in back yard perfect for your pets.  Plenty of back yard space for a garage! Home warranty is included - don't miss out on this one!
